body: @zhangqiang-hf, could you please verify if #9988 fix the build break? Please note that it only uses default scalar/pure C++ kernel and the performance will not be very good. To improve the perf, the SIMD version of kernel needs to be added just like what PowerPC did: https://github.com/microsoft/onnxruntime/blob/42c176b60c502ab3a26f7289397fa5cad5becba7/cmake/onnxruntime_mlas.cmake#L292.
